      of place.\n   - Character Design: Developing unique and memorable character
      designs that resonate with players and help bring the story to life.\n   -
      User Interface (UI) Design: Creatingitive and visually appealing UI that provides
      players with essential information and allows them to easily navigate the game.\n4.
      Sound Design:\n   - Music: Composing original music that sets the mood and
